snippet.title: MegaMan X: Corrupted - Cyber Lab
snippet.description:
I'm incredibly proud to share the amazing work the MMXC team has done!
Here’s some Zero gameplay in the Cyber Lab, which marks the seventh Maverick stage we've completed.

00:22 Start
00:49 Skill Tree 1
01:40 World Map
02:06 Cyber Lab Start
06:18 Cyber Lab Miniboss
07:44 Skill Tree 2
08:30 Cyber Lab Second Half
11:32 Warp Vulpex
16:08 Weapon Get
17:35 Cyber Gate
20:47 X vs Zero

Dev Team (order of entry)
- JKB
- Keiang (Artist / Writer) - https://www.youtube.com/@keiang3
- Genstov (Writer)
- Dominic Ninmark (Composer) - https://www.youtube.com/@DominicNinmark
- Voltbox (Artist) -  https://www.youtube.com/@SoojArt | https://x.com/SoojArt
- Kacper (Artist / Level Designer)
- Descense (Programmer / Artist)
- Patwick (Level Designer / Artist)
- Dink (Artist) - https://x.com/watashi_wa_dink
- Joshirostar (Artist / Composer / Sound) - https://www.youtube.com/@Joshirostar
- DioZv (Artist)

Collaborators
- Rishy (Artist)
- Eliloha (Artist)
- HombreRandom (Artist)
- Luminers(Artist)


Videos on Youtube are few and far between. If you would like to follow the project development and chat with the devs join us on our Discord community.
https://discord.com/servers/mmx-corrupted-276041301965668352

Project Wiki
https://jkbgames.com/w/index.php/MegaMan_X:_Corrupted_Wiki

** Disclaimer **
This is a Fan Game and not affiliated with Capcom.
Megaman X and all other megaman material are owned by Capcom.
